text: Behind these heroes we work to accelerate hospitals’ access to @sickbayMIC to deliver critical data at a safe distance.
Resolve. Courage. Hope. What's inside has never mattered more. Behind it all, we’re committed to accelerating access to tech that helps combat COVID-19.

Today, we are pledging $50 million in a Pandemic Response Technology Initiative to combat the coronavirus. We’re also including an innovation fund to fuel new ideas and ​technologies to reduce the impact of COVID-19.

Collaboration is key to conquering this pandemic. And the next. So we're working with @xprize & @AnthemInc to launch their COVID-19 response platform—all to help the global community unite in the fight.
Today we’re setting aside $6M for Coronavirus relief, building on our previous efforts of donating supplies to caregivers.
Now more than ever, healthcare workers need everyone’s support. So we’re sourcing and donating over 1 million personal protective items like masks and gloves for those on the front lines.
